name: Popular Painting by Wahyu F. Riyanto #3 on Tezos - Newyork At Night
description:
Newyork City View from above.
Digital Painting by an artist Wahyu F. Riyanto is created from photos taken by him. The photos from POPULAR locations or events in many different continents are transferred into beautiful digital painting by the artist. The initial drawings has made from photos taken in 27 countries, and keep counting. Also, the artist himself also a film director in his country. Another version of paintings also available on Opensea (Polygon ETH) marketplace please search Popular Painting by Wahyu F. Riyanto there
